headline.main: SHIPREPORT UNCONFIRMED; Berlin Says U.S. Supply Craft Hit Mine Off Vladivostok

abstract: Wash, London and Shanghai do not confirm Berlin radio rept that U S ship, carrying supplies to USSR, was damaged by mine off Vladivostok
